梨側から", "見る富士山の方が「表」って"]}, {"box": [176, 496, 206, 701], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[178.0, 496.0], [206.0, 496.0], [204.0, 701.0], [176.0, 701.0]]], "lines": ["よく言うよね"]}, {"box": [1091, 877, 1210, 1226], "vertical": true, "font_size": 34, "lines_coords": [[[1177.0, 881.0], [1209.0, 881.0], [1209.0, 1156.0], [1177.0, 1156.0]], [[1132.0, 877.0], [1170.0, 877.0], [1168.0, 1226.0], [1130.0, 1226.0]], [[1091.0, 879.0], [1123.0, 879.0], [1123.0, 1153.0], [1091.0, 1153.0]]], "lines": ["どっちも綺麗だし", "どっちが表でもいいと", "思うんだけどなぁ"]}, {"box": [761, 901, 898, 1140], "vertical": true, "font_size": 40, "lines_coords": [[[845.0, 903.0], [898.0, 903.0], [898.0, 1102.0], [845.0, 1102.0]], [[798.0, 901.0], [838.0, 901.0], [838.0, 1042.0], [798.0, 1042.0]], [[761.0, 903.0], [787.0, 903.0], [787.0, 1138.0], [761.0, 1138.0]]], "lines": ["シイッ！！", "アカンで", "なでしこちゃん"]}, {"box": [579, 889, 699, 1232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[665.0, 890.0], [697.0, 890.0], [697.0, 1065.0], [665.0, 1065.0]], [[620.0, 890.0], [652.0, 890.0], [652.0, 1231.0], [620.0, 1231.0]], [[579.0, 890.0], [611.0, 890.0], [611.0, 1061.0], [579.0, 1061.0]]], "lines": ["そないな事", "うちら以外の梨っ子に", "聞かれたら"]}, {"box": [159, 894, 207, 1318], "vertical": true, "font_size": 45, "lines_coords": [[[159.0, 894.0], [204.0, 894.0], [204.0, 1318.0], [159.0, 1318.0]]], "lines": ["大変な事になるで！！"]}, {"box": [230, 1623, 277, 1728], "vertical": true, "font_size": 47, "lines_coords": [[[230.0, 1623.0], [277.0, 1623.0], [277.0, 1728.0], [230.0, 1728.0]]], "lines": ["え？"]}], "img_path": "00161.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [1123, 146, 1191, 394], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[1158.0, 148.0], [1190.0, 148.0], [1190.0, 333.0], [1158.0, 333.0]], [[1123.0, 150.0], [1149.0, 150.0], [1149.0, 393.0], [1123.0, 393.0]]], "lines": ["表ではあまり", "知られとらんけど"]}, {"box": [647, 134, 756, 510], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[